</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Create the Logic Block</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Name: WriteProducts</p><p>Table: Your Product=
s table</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Write the Logic</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>We will break the logic into two parts: inser=
t, update</p><p>Insert:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>If the Logic Block Mode =3D Create, do the following actions</p></li=
>
<li><p>Insert the values into the table</p></li>
</ul><p>Update:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>If the Logic Block Mode =3D Edit, do the following actions</p></li>
<li><p>Values are passed in to update a product. If the <code>nwId</code> i=
s missing, set an error - use the <code>nsTrnMASTERMsg5</code> Data Item.</=
p></li>
<li><p>Update the fetched record</p></li>
</ul><p>Notes:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>While an Action Block is responsible for the insert, update, and del=
ete, the platform still validates the table pieces including required field=
s, filtered table lookups, and indexes. </p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>:warning:<em><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,19=
6,0);">Checkpoint</span></em></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li><p>Make sure the LB is saved.</p></li>
<li><p>You check if the Logic Block Mode =3D Create. If so, you are inserti=
ng into the products table.</p></li>
<li><p>You check if the Logic Block Mode =3D Edit. If so, you are validatin=
g that a parameter is passed in and then updating the record. </p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Attaching to the table</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li><p>Go to your products table definition. </p></li>
<li><p>In the General Configuration tab, add two rows to the Action Blocks =
subtable</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Insert</p></li>
<li><p>Update</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul><p>Do not add a value for the Delete action. We will let the platform =
to handle deletes.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>:warning:<em><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,19=
6,0);">Checkpoint</span></em></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li><p>You are able to insert a record</p></li>
<li><p>You are able to update a record</p></li>
<li><p>You receive the proper errors based on the validations</p></li>
